00:17:59,440 --> 00:18:00,440
If you start with i, after a time it's U of t.

258
00:18:00,440 --> 00:18:01,440
And then you start with i.

259
00:18:01,440 --> 00:18:04,440
After a time it's U of t of i.

260
00:18:04,440 --> 00:18:15,440
j evolves with the Hermitian conjugate of U, j.

261
00:18:15,440 --> 00:18:19,440
And the assumption is that if i and j were orthonormal,

