00:40:04,440 --> 00:40:07,440
Now the order that you write down

666
00:40:07,440 --> 00:40:09,440
a and the Poisson bracket,

667
00:40:09,440 --> 00:40:10,440
that's not important.

668
00:40:10,440 --> 00:40:11,440
These are just numbers.

669
00:40:11,440 --> 00:40:14,440
I mean, these are just ordinary functions or numbers,

